~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : rmail                                     ~FTPODnuts Revision
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : rmail [message number]
		  : rmail new

   This lists out your mailbox to you.
   Adding a number as argument shows that specific msg.
   To just read new mail, use .rmail new

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : smail, dmail, from
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

